# рџ“– About the Project

**RoadRush** is a console-based 2D car racing game developed entirely in **C++** using the **Windows Console API**.

Players enter their name, choose a car, customize its color, and race through endless traffic while avoiding collisions and earning points. As the score increases, the game becomes progressively more challenging by increasing enemy speed.

This project was built to strengthen programming fundamentals while applying **Object-Oriented Programming**, **game development concepts**, **file handling**, and **Windows multimedia libraries** without using any external game engine.

---

