- рџ“– Instructions menu for new players
- рџЋ® Smooth keyboard controls
- рџ›ЈпёЏ Endless arcade-style gameplay

---

# рџ“љ Object-Oriented Programming Concepts Used

| OOP Concept | Implementation |
|-------------|----------------|
| **Classes & Objects** | `Car`, `Enemy`, `Game`, `Utils` |
| **Encapsulation** | Private data members accessed through public methods |
| **Constructors** | Parameterized constructors with default values |
| **Abstraction** | Rendering, collision detection, and game logic hidden behind methods |
| **Composition** | `Game` contains `Car` and `Enemy` objects |
| **Static Members** | Utility functions implemented as static methods |
| **Modular Programming** | Game functionality separated into reusable functions |

