---

# рџљЂ How to Run

### Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/zainab-rehmann/RoadRush-CPP.git
cd RoadRush-CPP
```

### Configure Dev-C++

Open:

```
Project
в†“
Project Options
в†“
Parameters
```

Add under **Linker**:

```
-lwinmm
```

Enable compiler options:

```
-static-libgcc
-std=c++11
```

### Compile using MinGW

```bash
g++ RoadRush.cpp -o RoadRush -lwinmm
```

### Required Audio Files

Place the following files in the same directory as `RoadRush.exe`:

- car_background.mp3
- car_move_left.wav
- car_move_right.wav
- mixkit-car-start-ignition-1559.wav
- score_point.wav

### Run

```
RoadRush.exe
```

